DESCRIPTION:Join us on Sunday\, June 21\, for free outdoor mat Pilates led by Revival Pilates. This evening class begins at 6 p.m. at Molly Ann Smith Plaza\, adjacent to McGovern Lake and the Pioneer Memorial Obelisk. Be sure to bring a mat and water. \nYou must sign up to attend! Book your spot HERE.
