SUMMARY:Wellness Walk
DESCRIPTION:Join Laura Conely of Urban Paths for a fun evening as we explore the trails and beauty of Hermann Park on a guided 3-mile experience. All are invited to this conversationally paced walk; friendly pups on leash are welcome too! \nThis event is free\, but registration is required and space is limited. Sign up HERE. Participants will meet outside the McGovern Centennial Gardens\, located at 1500 Hermann Drive\, with parking available in adjacent Lot C. \nLaura Conely is the founder of Urban Paths\, a walking wellness company. As a certified teacher and coach\, she leads guided Wellness Walks that bring individuals of all ages and fitness levels together to experience the profound health benefits of: Nature\, Art\, Movement\, and Connection.
URL:https://hermannpark.org/event/wellness-walk-8/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/P1010158-Voltz-Photography-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
