SUMMARY:Red\, White & Cruise
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Red\, White & Cruise where you can watch Miller Outdoor Theatre’s fireworks show light up the sky from the peaceful waters of Hermann Park\, with a special pedal boat rental from 8:30–10:30 p.m. on Saturday\, July 4! 🎇 \nAs we celebrate 250 years of American independence\, gather your crew and watch the sky come alive with fireworks while cruising across the lake in your own pedal boat under the stars. 🌟  \nSaturday\, July 4\n8:30 – 10:30 p.m.  \n🎟️ $150 per boat (up to 4 people) includes:\n🕘 Boat rental up to 2 hours\n🍿 Drinks & snacks\n🎊 Festive accessories\n🅿️ Reserved parking in Lot I near Lake Plaza\n⛵ Board anytime between 8:30–9:30 p.m. and enjoy the show from the water (fireworks begin at approximately 9:45 p.m.\, boats must return once fireworks finish) \nBOOK YOUR BOAT HERE!  \n🚨 Important Info: \n\nOne rider per boat must be 18+\nAll riders 18+ must sign a digital waiver before boarding\nAt least one rider must be 18+\, with a physical government ID\, and sign a waiver before boarding\nTickets are non-refundable\nEvent is rain or shine per Miller Outdoor Theatre’s plan\nIn the event of lightning\, pedal boats will close\, and refunds will be issued \n\nThe purchase of a ticket includes an up-to 2-hour pedal boat ride for up to 4 people to enjoy the sight of Miller Outdoor Theatre’s fireworks show\, drinks\, snacks\, festive treats\, and a reserved parking spot in Lot I near Lott Hall by Lake Plaza (starting at 8 p.m.). Only one ticket purchase of $150 is needed for a 4-person boat (i.e. it is the cost per boat\, not per rider).  \nA reminder that at least one rider per boat must be 18 years or older.  All riders 18 years or older must sign a digital waiver before boarding. Tickets are non-refundable. We are following Miller Outdoor Theatre’s plan for their event and fireworks show which is rain or shine. If there is lightning in the area\, we will close the pedal boats and ticket holders will receive a refund.  \nPlease arrive early to allow time to park in Lot I as roads in the Park will be closed by HPD and closures are subject to change based on their purview.  
URL:https://hermannpark.org/event/red-white-cruise-2/
LOCATION:Lake Plaza
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Red-White-Cruise-2026.jpg
END:VEVENT
