SUMMARY:Japanese Garden Volunteer Day
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Thursday for hands-on gardening projects at the Japanese Garden. From 9 a.m. to 12 p.m.\, come help with seasonal tasks like planting\, weeding\, mulching\, and pruning. A great way to connect with others and make a visible impact in the Park! \nNo experience needed. All ages are welcome. \nClick here to sign up!
